{"TopicId":160275,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Amazing free mercury capsule sim with interactive cockpits and VR support! Anyone tried it?","CreatedByName":"moonlandermike","CreatedById":177524,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-06T18:32:48Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"moonlandermike","CreatedById":177524,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-06T18:32:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m fairly sure its ok to post this as it seems to be free with an option to fund (seems to fit the forum guidelines!)...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve\u00A0just stumbled on this little gem and I\u0027m blown away that it\u0027s apparently made by just one guy! \u00A0Has anyone tried it? \u00A0It looks like it\u0027s still in alpha but already looks great and even has support for VR headsets (like I dream about for KSP \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyway, free download links here for PC and Mac -\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/go-for-launch-mercury-vr-educational#/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.indiegogo.com/projects/go-for-launch-mercury-vr-educational#/\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0 You can just ignore all the bits about crowdfunding (although I think I\u0027ll drop some money to support the effort!).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt doesn\u0027t really seem to tread on KSP\u0027s toes as it\u0027s a different kind of game, a bit more like Orbiter crossed with A-OK (anyone ever play that?).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/dCa8npC.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022dCa8npC.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/bpMWI3q.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022bpMWI3q.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/mdl9Wtk.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022mdl9Wtk.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ten Key","CreatedById":123319,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-06T19:25:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe developer working on this is actually on this forum. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/119139-new-mercury-simulator-coming-out-soon-this-is-why-i-have-so-little-time-for-ksp-modding-now/\u0026amp;\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Raging Sandwich","CreatedById":164377,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-06T20:17:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo ipsEmbeddedVideo_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/sEAYakClECU?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NSEP","CreatedById":165635,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-06T20:22:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223047340\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160275\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221494101844\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022164377\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Raging Sandwich\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, The Raging Sandwich said